<title>Change Map Intervals</title>

<list ordered>
	<li>From the <b>Format</b> menu, select <b>Legend</b>; or press <b>Ctrl+L</b>; or right click on the legend. The Legend dialog box will appear.</li>
	<li>You may select the number of groups, the lower and upper limits of each group, and the text to appear with each group.</li>
</list>

You can also right click on the legend on the screen (if not hidden) to get to the Legend dialog box.
